@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Volunteer";
}

<div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="text-center fw-bold">Volunteer With Us</h1>
    <p class="text-center lead">Make a difference in the lives of animals by volunteering your time and skills.</p>

    <div class="mt-5">
        <h3>🐾 Why Volunteer?</h3>
        <p>Volunteering is a rewarding experience that allows you to help animals in need, support shelter operations, and make a positive impact in your community.</p>

        <h3>💡 How You Can Help</h3>
        <p>There are many ways to contribute as a volunteer. Whether you have a few hours a week or a few days a month, your time makes a big difference.</p>

        <h4>🏡 Shelter Support</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Cleaning and maintaining pet areas</li>
            <li>Helping with feeding and grooming</li>
            <li>Assisting with adoption events</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>🐕 Animal Care</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Walking and exercising dogs</li>
            <li>Socializing with pets to improve their behavior</li>
            <li>Providing basic training for adoptable pets</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>📢 Community Outreach</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Raising awareness about pet adoption</li>
            <li>Organizing fundraising events</li>
            <li>Helping with social media and marketing</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>📞 Contact Us</h3>
        <p>If you’re interested in volunteering, reach out to us for more details.</p>

        <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li><strong>📍 Location:</strong> 54, Jalan Pandan Indah, Cheras, Selangor</li>
            <li><strong>📧 Email:</strong> <a href="Admin@PetAdoption.org">Admin@PetAdoption.org</a></li>
            <li><strong>📞 Phone:</strong> (123) 456-7890</li>
            <li><strong>⏰ Volunteer Hours:</strong> Monday - Saturday | 9 AM - 5 PM</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-5 text-center">
        <h3>Ready to Make a Difference?</h3>
        <p>Contact us today to learn how you can help!</p>
        <a href="/Contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
</div>
